item.description:

Dillinger is a cloud-enabled, mobile-ready, offline-storage, AngularJS powered HTML5 Markdown editor. Type some Markdown on the left See HTML in the right Magic New Features! Import a HTML file and watch it magically convert to Markdown Drag and drop images (requires your Dropbox account be linked)
